        &lt;prefer-application-packages&gt;
            &lt;package-name&gt;org.opensaml.*&lt;/package-name&gt;
        &lt;/prefer-application-packages&gt;

maybe `&lt;prefer-web-inf-classes&gt;true&lt;/prefer-web-inf-classes&gt;` would work too.

